<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Tachau</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Heinrich Reck, Bürger zu Nürnberg, wegen des Geleits für die in Tachau aufgehaltenen Kaufmannszüge aus Nürnberg nach Böhmen an und bittet sie um Fürsprache bei Sulko, Propst von Chotieschau.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_452" id="225v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_452_r1l18">Der Stat cʒu Tachaw </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_452_r1l19"><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan> <expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan> vns hat der Erwirdig <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / her Sulco probſt cʒu Chotiſchaw </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l20">vnd hauptman cʒu Tachaw nehſt <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vvılle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l21">den Er cʒu vns <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> Stat / vnd den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hab / vvol cʒu verſteen <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l22">Alſo <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> etliche <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>e</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> vnd kauffleute auf <expan>ſolch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> troſte </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l23">etliche Jr habe vnd kauffmanſchaft hinein gen Beheim geſchıckt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l24">dıe cʒu ew gen Tachaw <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey vnd do lig Als ſie vns geſagt <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l25">die ſie gern fürbaʒ bringen wolten / Möchten ſie das vor vnfride </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l26">getun / vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darümb dem <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Recken <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> <expan>beuolhe<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l27">mit dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Sulco </del> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> probſte cʒu reden / vvie man </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l28"><expan>dieſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab vnd kauffmanſchaft <expan>furbaʒ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ſich<ex>er</ex></expan> bringen müge </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l29">vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr <expan>demſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günſtige fürdrunge </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l30">gen dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> probſt beweẏſen vnd auch darẏnne </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l31">geraten vnd hilfflich ſein wöllet / daʒ dieſelb hab vnd <expan>kauffma<ex>n</ex>ſ<ex>chaft</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l32"><expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan> <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> des probſts gepite <expan>ſich<ex>er</ex></expan> geleytet werde </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_452_r1l33">Als etc / das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ııj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Ph<ex>ilippi</ex></expan> et Jacobi </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_452" id="225v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der stat czu Tachaw </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde,</ex></expan> uns hat der erwirdig
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> her Sulco, probst czu Chotischaw und
                        hauptman czu Tachaw, nehst <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                                <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>gute<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>, den er czu uns,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat und den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> hab, wol czu versteen
                                <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; also <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        etliche <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>e</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> und kauffleute auf
                            <expan>solch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> troste etliche ir habe und
                        kauffmanschaft hinein gen Beheim geschickt, die czu ew gen Tachaw
                                <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> sey und do lig, als sie uns gesagt
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n,</expan> die sie gern fürbaz bringen wolten,
                        möchten sie das vor unfride getun; und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> darümb
                        dem <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Recken, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r,</ex></expan>
<expan>bevolhe<ex>n,</ex></expan> mit dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> probste czu reden, wie man
                                <expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hab und kauffmanschaft
                                <expan>furbaz<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>sich<ex>er</ex></expan> bringen müge. Und
                            <expan>ro<ex>gamus,</ex></expan> daz ir
                            <expan>demselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günstige fürdrunge gen dem
                                <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan> probst, beweysen
                        und auch darynne geraten und hilfflich sein wöllet, daz dieselb hab und
                                <expan>kauffma<ex>n</ex>s<ex>chaft</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>ur</ex>h</expan>
<expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, des probsts, gepite
                            <expan>sich<ex>er</ex></expan> geleytet werde, als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iii <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Ph<ex>ilippi</ex></expan> et Jacobi.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
